If the kmalloc() fails in mantis_pci_probe() you don't call 
pci_disable_device(). And you should kzalloc() instead of kmalloc() and 
memset().
It looks like you never use "__u16 vendor_id;" and "__u16 device_id;" in 
struct mantis_pci.
